snippet.title: Slap City released for Early Access
snippet.description:
Get it now dog dangit!

SLAP CITY is Ludosity's new platform fighting game. Now available for early access while we add more of all the characters you know and love and also some other stuff. Check it out!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/725480/Slap_City/
http://www.slapcity.se/
